<plot>Remembering his wife Lenore who died at an early age, Edgar descends into depression going in and out of reality overwhelmed with memories of his lost love. He is then visited by a raven that offers him nothing but advice and forces him to not forget the past but move forward in the future. Time passes and Edgar realizes that the raven is a figment of his imagination. He then decides to honor his wife's last wishes, to move on living life to the fullest.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?585472</url></doc>
